column3: Greetings, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>! How might I be of service?
That strange girl you met in the Empty is in our custody.
Her location is a closely guarded secret, and she is being monitored night and day for any changes in her condition.

We have also been treating any information regarding your mission as strictly confidential. It would cause quite a stir amongst the peoples of Norvrandt were it to become public knowledge, and we cannot afford for anyone to interfere with our work.

Fortunately, the majority of the tasks we perform─such as delivering supplies and equipment─tend to go unnoticed for the most part. In order to maintain this status quo, I and my colleagues will continue to lend our support in as discreet a manner as possible.
